Cash>>> from me to you

Hi customers. My store will be closed temporarily. All orders have been completed and if I am discussing a deal with you I will keep myself available. We are updating inventory as with Superdollars looking unlikely we wish to expand into very high quality euros in their place. Thanks for your understanding and keep it minty.

Terms

These are the terms of my store. They are the first thing you see for a reason. If you don't like them there are other fish in the sea. If you decide to do business with my store, and then break these terms, your emails and other missives will be ignored.

My store offers genuine counterfeit currency. We currently only offer USD as we like keep to what we know. Our asking price is normally around 50% of the face value of your order. The notes can be the denomination of your choice, but understand that lower denominations will cost more. Full, independent escrow is accepted. You can chose which one, but it must be reliable.

I will not upload images or other "proofs". This is bullshit. Anyone can download an image of the web and then offer it up as proof. It is very easy to edit or spoof an image anyway. This makes uploaded images useless to you. They are also dangerous to us . Images contain metadata, and metadata if not removed properly can fuck up ones anonymity. Research it yourself if you don't trust this information. Do not ask us for image proofs.

I will not send free samples. If you want to use my time and my product then pay me. Also I am not a charity, and if you think it is clever to ask a criminal to act like a charity then I truly pity you. Don't email me stories about how your mothers pet crocodile died and how your family has been bankrupted by the cost of a pet crocodile funeral to try to get me to donate product. I don't care about your situation.

These notes won't work in banks or ATMs. Just don't try it. They are high quality, but they are not real and a bank will be able to spot them. No one can produce counterfeits that would pass in a bank. They will work in clubs, shops and just about anywhere else that accept notes. There are good guides on passing counterfeits around the web. Read them.

These notes should not be used with real notes. I understand the urge to blend in a few fake notes with a bunch of real ones. Resist the urge. It makes the fake ones look really really fake.

I am not going to provide any further guidance than that which is offered here. To benefit from my service you need to know what you are doing. If you don't then you need to learn before buying. I don't babysit.

I can refuse to work with you without providing a reason if I am uncomfortable.

I will not try to deceive you, so be honest with me. It really isn't hard, and being on Tor is not an invitation to act like a dick.

Agree and proceed
